      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GREAT TERMS (6) doesn't show much early dash but winds into his races, hitting the line hard to score two back then came home strongly into second (30.19) in a Grade 5 at this track last time. Solid record here at the distance winning three races. Top prospect. MALAWI REBEL (8) sailed across from an outside draw last start to score an all-the-way win (29.85) at this track in a Grade 5 over 520m. Comes through a solid form race last start. Sure to be thereabouts. AUSSIE ZIP (5) flew around 366m at Capalaba in 19.86 three back then has been in the money the last two since. Smart winner three back and looks a key chance on that form. FIRE TEARS (1) proved himself from this box last start so warrants respect.",
